content.p: You can use our online booking system to book your sports massage appointment at our Sports Injury Clinic. For all other appointments, please email us at sportsinjuries@nottingham.ac.uk or call us on +44 115 74 87070. You can use our online portal to book and manage your sports massage appointments. Online booking for other services will be coming soon. If you are having trouble access our online booking portal, please try visit this website instead or contact us by emailing sportsinjuries@nottingham.ac.uk.
